    <item>
      <title>“一场缓慢滚动的灾难”：普拉特纳竞选活动的内爆</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/08/us/politics/graham-platner-campaign-implosion-maine.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格雷厄姆·普拉特纳竞选参议员激励了进步的民主党人。但周三他暂停的竞选活动却混乱无序，最终因丑闻不断而注定失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/08/us/politics/graham-platner-campaign-implosion-maine.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 02:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>性侵犯指控会扼杀政治生涯吗？这取决于。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/08/us/politics/democrats-republicans-sexual-assault-politicians.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格雷厄姆·普拉特纳(Graham Platner)迅速退出缅因州参议员竞选，埃里克·斯瓦尔韦尔(Eric Swalwell)也退出加州州长竞选，但共和党采取了不同的策略。]]></description>
