      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/07/us/politics/graham-platner-replacements-maine-democrats.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[甚至在普拉特纳暂停竞选之前，几名缅因州民主党人就表示有兴趣竞选参议员。]]></description>
