    <item>
      <title>安全预防措施导致特朗普使用旧空军一号离开土耳其</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/08/us/politics/trump-air-force-one-security.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据说特勤局要求总统在离开安卡拉时不要使用卡塔尔捐赠的飞机。这次交换加深了有关新飞机改装的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/08/us/politics/trump-air-force-one-security.html</guid>
